author: Business Insider
description:
At a time when volatility is the norm, procurement leaders are being asked to do more than keep the lights on. They're navigating macroeconomic headwinds, regulatory complexity, climate risks, and fragile supply chains. But instead of simply reacting, the most forward-thinking teams are using this moment to transform.

Business Insider will explore this inflection point at a virtual event on July 30 at Noon ET, titled Resilient Growth: Navigating Procurement Complexity.
